WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug
needs the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your “same here”
carries a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is
what truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.287
=Episode 10=

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.520
What's wrong?

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:10.560
See someone you know?

00:01:12.120 --> 00:01:15.000
No. Not really.

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:22.440
She's here.

00:01:27.300 --> 00:01:28.720
Let me introduce you.

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:29.900
Lily Fan.

00:01:29.962 --> 00:01:32.320
Let's welcome her to
the Pioneers Alliance, alright?

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:32.800
Yes!

00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:35.840
(Gathering at Yitang)
Welcome!

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:36.640
Come.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:37.960
Let's sit.

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:42.160
Welcome.

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:43.200
Let me toast you.

00:01:43.960 --> 00:01:45.720
Let's toast her together.

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:48.440
Raise our glasses together.
Let's drink to taking down the Lu Group.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:50.240
Cheers!

00:01:53.987 --> 00:01:56.587
How about I take you somewhere else?

00:01:56.900 --> 00:01:58.460
Let's go eat steak.

00:02:00.037 --> 00:02:02.997
It's fine. I like this place.

00:02:03.240 --> 00:02:04.237
We'll stay.

00:02:04.962 --> 00:02:06.092
Cheers.

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:13.040
Try this.

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:19.520
A toast to you.

00:02:20.660 --> 00:02:22.440
Thank you for letting me join
the company.

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:24.400
I'll work hard.

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:28.080
I know what you're capable of.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:29.320
Thank you.

00:02:35.040 --> 00:02:36.640
You're still the same.

00:02:37.112 --> 00:02:39.152
Hot and cold.

00:02:39.737 --> 00:02:43.297
Anyone else would think you're strange.

00:02:43.297 --> 00:02:44.937
But not me.

00:02:44.937 --> 00:02:46.390
That's exactly what I like about you.

00:02:48.187 --> 00:02:49.627
I'm going to the restroom.

00:02:49.630 --> 00:02:50.740
We'll drink more when I'm back.

00:02:50.740 --> 00:02:52.060
Alright?

00:02:52.060 --> 00:02:53.580
Keep her company.

00:02:53.580 --> 00:02:55.500
Excuse me.

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:58.200
Mr. Ye picked this place.

00:02:58.200 --> 00:02:59.840
(Gathering at Yitang)
Better than anywhere we've eaten before.

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:03.200
You guys eat.

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:04.012
I'll check on him.

00:03:04.012 --> 00:03:04.812
Okay.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:14.560
The new colleagues are great.

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:21.560
Why can't you hold your liquor well now?

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:22.680
A few beers and you're done.

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:25.400
I'm not drunk.

00:03:26.280 --> 00:03:28.920
I'm just happy
for the Pioneers Alliance.

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:32.760
Man,

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:36.960
you still have feelings for me,
don't you?

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:50.080
Zhu?

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:55.240
I don't want to leave you again.

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:11.880
Clean this up. Quick.

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:14.520
Lily,

00:04:15.480 --> 00:04:16.640
we've broken up.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:18.480
Don't do this.

00:04:19.880 --> 00:04:22.240
Man, I was immature before.

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:25.600
I admit that I thought staying
in the project team

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:27.360
or the US mattered more
than anything to me.

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:29.440
But I don't think that way anymore.

00:04:29.440 --> 00:04:31.560
Can we start over?

00:04:32.137 --> 00:04:34.297
Come on, drink.

00:04:34.350 --> 00:04:36.080
Let's toast her together.

00:04:36.080 --> 00:04:36.880
Together.

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:37.880
Drink.

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.600
You don't have to answer me now.

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.840
I know you're still single.

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:47.480
This time, I'll be the one chasing you.

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:53.040
You still haven't had enough.

00:04:55.762 --> 00:04:57.462
Nobody's skipping drinks, got it?

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:05.000
Zhu?

00:05:06.400 --> 00:05:07.960
What's wrong?

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:09.520
Why are you crying all of a sudden?

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:14.400
Look at me. Come on.

00:05:14.525 --> 00:05:15.950
I'll cheer you up.

00:05:15.950 --> 00:05:17.160
I can make some funny faces.

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:18.080
Look at me.

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.562
How's it? I'll cheer you up.

00:05:19.562 --> 00:05:20.362
Watch closely.

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:24.480
I'll do another one.

00:06:11.920 --> 00:06:12.840
Take them away!

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:19.600
What has happened, Mr. Lu?

00:06:20.037 --> 00:06:22.397
Zhu didn't come home last night.

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:23.880
Do you know where she went?

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:25.600
What do you mean?

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:26.400
Zhu is missing?

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:28.040
Did she say anything to you

00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:29.760
when you saw her?

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:30.800
No.

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:32.100
What?

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:34.600
You can't find her anywhere?

00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:35.840
Listen up.

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:37.812
Turn the entire Hai City upside down

00:06:37.812 --> 00:06:39.280
to find her. Now!

00:06:39.840 --> 00:06:41.080
Don't panic.

00:06:41.137 --> 00:06:43.497
Has Lu been acting strange lately?

00:06:43.497 --> 00:06:45.097
Did she meet anyone new?

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:47.440
Or did she start dating?

00:06:47.800 --> 00:06:49.920
As far as I know,
Zhu doesn't have a boyfriend.

00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:51.440
So I don't think this is simple.

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:52.640
Man is right.

00:06:53.300 --> 00:06:54.900
Zhu may be spoiled,

00:06:54.900 --> 00:06:56.737
but she's always been well-behaved.

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:58.440
She's never stayed out all night.

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:01.280
Could it be the company...

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:07.000
Mr. Lu, I found this in the mailbox.

00:07:08.887 --> 00:07:09.720
Tianze?

00:07:12.880 --> 00:07:15.160
See? I told you.

00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:16.400
Lu is dating someone.

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.880
Alright, everything's fine.

00:07:19.880 --> 00:07:20.720
Go to work now.

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:29.360
Chen, where's your son?

00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:31.520
Call him.

00:07:31.520 --> 00:07:33.520
Tell him to send my daughter back
immediately.

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:34.520
Stop messing around!

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:36.800
No more next time.

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:48.920
Would they dock the boss's pay
if he slacks off at work?

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:53.880
Yes, they would.

00:07:55.890 --> 00:07:57.075
What's wrong with you today?

00:07:57.075 --> 00:07:57.915
You're distracted.

00:08:01.510 --> 00:08:03.072
My sister didn't come home last night.

00:08:05.487 --> 00:08:06.562
Your stepsister?

00:08:09.037 --> 00:08:12.157
Lily, do girls like the type

00:08:13.687 --> 00:08:15.247
who go out with a big group of friends

00:08:15.887 --> 00:08:18.127
and act like street punks in movies?

00:08:19.320 --> 00:08:21.240
Must've watched too many gangster films.

00:08:24.300 --> 00:08:25.100
I think so too.

00:08:27.062 --> 00:08:28.222
What's so great about him?

00:08:35.800 --> 00:08:36.760
Man,

00:08:37.337 --> 00:08:40.897
who your sister dates
is none of your business.

00:08:41.737 --> 00:08:43.337
You should focus on the project.

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:47.960
I just received news.

00:08:48.760 --> 00:08:51.400
We're not the only company
at the roadshow.

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:55.200
The Lu Group found you
a strong competitor.

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:58.600
A local tech company,
Mobiyun Technology.

00:08:59.880 --> 00:09:02.040
They'll also attend the roadshow.

00:09:02.040 --> 00:09:04.787
The higher vote wins Tang Group's
funding for the next two years.

00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:07.560
So

00:09:08.700 --> 00:09:10.020
you can't let your guard down.

00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:16.560
You're right.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:19.000
Give me the contract.

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:20.360
It's on your desk.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:43.200
Chen?

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:44.520
When are you coming back?

00:09:44.520 --> 00:09:46.320
Your son's got some nerve.

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:47.800
How dare he touch my daughter!

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:49.880
I've already sent people out.

00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:51.790
We'll dig three feet into the ground
if we have to.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:53.520
Don't worry.

00:09:53.680 --> 00:09:54.280
Enough.

00:09:54.280 --> 00:09:54.920
I'm telling you,

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:57.080
Zhu better be fine.

00:09:57.380 --> 00:09:59.240
If a single hair on her head
is harmed, you...

00:09:59.280 --> 00:10:00.680
Lu, once I find that rascal,

00:10:00.680 --> 00:10:02.360
I'll make him kneel
and apologize to you.

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:04.440
Let's go.

00:10:13.150 --> 00:10:14.650
Let go!

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:18.720
You're the one

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:20.840
who got Jia locked up.

00:10:20.840 --> 00:10:22.990
When you beat a dog,
you should check its owner first.

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:25.080
Do you know whose man you touched?

00:10:25.400 --> 00:10:28.040
He got caught drag racing.

00:10:28.440 --> 00:10:30.600
What's that got to do with me?

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:32.162
Don't get cocky, rascal.

00:10:32.437 --> 00:10:33.560
Everyone knows

00:10:33.560 --> 00:10:35.480
I've been in Hai City for years

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:38.680
for a big...

00:10:40.600 --> 00:10:41.440
Big what again?

00:10:43.480 --> 00:10:45.800
A big fish, boss.

00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:47.200
A big fish?

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:53.240
Don't touch her!

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:54.960
Come at me if you've got guts!

00:11:04.040 --> 00:11:05.280
What?

00:11:05.280 --> 00:11:06.360
Scared I'll touch her?

00:11:06.400 --> 00:11:07.360
Listen.

00:11:07.360 --> 00:11:08.760
If you dare touch her again,

00:11:08.920 --> 00:11:11.037
I'll fight you to the death!

00:11:14.037 --> 00:11:15.037
Got some backbone, huh?

00:11:16.137 --> 00:11:17.950
Do you play pool?

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:25.280
How about this?

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:26.480
If you win,

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:27.680
I won't touch

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:31.280
your girl.

00:12:52.037 --> 00:12:52.837
Wait.

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.800
Let's make it harder.

00:13:06.287 --> 00:13:07.407
Go on.

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:10.960
If you sink the shot,
I'll let your girl go.

00:13:41.160 --> 00:13:42.400
Such audacity!

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:43.040
Beat him.

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:44.640
Beat the crap out of him!

00:14:08.112 --> 00:14:12.612
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:14:12.837 --> 00:14:16.625
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:14:16.800 --> 00:14:20.875
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:14:20.875 --> 00:14:25.012
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:14:25.137 --> 00:14:28.912
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:14:28.912 --> 00:14:32.687
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

00:14:32.687 --> 00:14:34.962
♪The you in my memories♪

00:14:34.962 --> 00:14:36.975
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:14:36.975 --> 00:14:42.412
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:14:43.975 --> 00:14:49.412
♪Forget you completely?♪